  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to show clinically meaningful improvement in symptom severity
      after trans-nasal balloon dilation of the maxillary sinus outflow tract with or without
      balloon dilation of the frontal or sphenoid sinuses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
